          <text>
                    <body>
                              <pb n="1"/>
                              <p rend="align(right)"><placeName>Charleston, S. C.</placeName>
                                        <date>May 2. 1853</date>.</p>
                              <p><addressee>Rev. I. Leeser</addressee>,
                                                  <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>.</p>
                              <p rend="indent(1)">My dear Sir! About 3 weeks ago I addressed<lb/> a
                                        letter to you, and must now suppose, that it has been<lb/>
                                        miscarried, as I have not yet received any answer of
                                                  <add>?</add>,<lb/> nor the Occident, for which I
                                        have requested you in that letter.<lb/> I therefore would
                                        herewith repeat the contents of that letter,<lb/> as far as
                                        my recollection serves me.</p>
                              <p rend="indent(1)">Being desirous of receiving the Occident
                                        regularly,<lb/> you will send the same, commencing with the
                                                  <date>April</date> No every<lb/> month to my
                                        direction, and forward me your bill, through<lb/> your agent
                                        in this city,m at your earliest convenience.</p>
                              <p rend="indent(1)">A friend of mine having presented me with a<lb/>
                                        full set of the Occident, You would oblige me very much<lb/>
                                        by sending me No 1. of Vol. VI. the only missing<lb/>
                                        number.</p>
                              <p rend="indent(1)">At the same time I would announce to you,
                                        that<lb/> I have, on <date>Pureem</date>, been engaged to
                                                  <persName>Miss Rachel Ottolengin</persName>,<lb/>
                                        daughter of the late <persName>Mr. Ottolengin,
                                                  Esq.</persName>—</p>
                              <p rend="indent(1)">Things are going on, in both our congr., very
                                        quietly, and<lb/> thank God—<sic>peacably</sic>; my
                                        colleague, <persName>Rev. Jacobs</persName> preaches<lb/>
                                        orthodoxy, my humble self reform, <del>both</del> but we
                                        live else on<lb/> the most friendly terms.—The former
                                        however is now a<lb/> little vexed about <persName>Mr
                                                  Lyons</persName>, who has charged him<lb/> $15.50
                                        for the publication of his letter against you, and</p>
                              <pb n="2"/>
                              <p>would not publish his rejoinder to your reply—covering 28
                                        foolscap—<lb/>pages—unless paid for with $50.00. The
                                        independent<lb/> paper!!!</p>
                              <p rend="indent(5)">Please accept my best regards</p>
                              <p rend="indent(6)">Yours most respectfully</p>
                              <p rend="indent(7)">
                                        <persName role="author">Dr M Mayer</persName>
                              </p>
                              <pb n="3"/>
                              <p><addressee>Rev. I. Leeser</addressee>,</p>
                              <p rend="indent(1)">
                                        <placeName>371. Walnut str.</placeName>
                              </p>
                              <p rend="indent(1)">
                                        <placeName><hi rend="underline">Philadelphia,</hi>
                                                  Pa.</placeName>
                              </p>
